title: PT 2: We Can't Believe This Guy Unknowingly Had A Convo With An A-List Celeb!
description:
You meet a stranger at a bar, and they become your new friend. You two talk for over three hours before they leave. Afterward, someone walks up to you and asks if you know who that person is. They reveal it was an A-list celebrity.
Has this ever happened to you? If so, we want to hear from you!
